{
 "name": "RPlog_Retribution_-_Defending_the_Malevolence",
 "title": "Retribution: Defending the Malevolence",
 "summary": "Spurred by the loss of Palliata Station and continued destruction on the ground, New Republic officers launch a bold strike force to test the Imperial flagship Malevolence herself and gather intelligence. The Fusillade and her entourage -- the Carracks Redstar and Jack Cade in the vanguard with supporting corvettes -- push into the Imperial fleet, with pilots like Alex and Aramis in the fray. The audacious raid pits the Republic's forward line against the mighty Malevolence in a high-stakes engagement amid the ongoing battle of retribution over Coruscant.",
